Right to withdraw consent
:
If we rely on your consent as our legal basis for processing your Personal Data, you have the right to withdraw that consent at any time.
Right to lodge a complaint with the data protection authority
:
If you have a concern about any aspect of our privacy practices, including the way we have handled your Personal Data, you can report it to the data protection authority that is authorized to hear those concerns.
